                    <h3 id="class-desc">HTTP Error Codes</h3>
                    <p>Below are the standard HTTP Error Codes that the Resgrid API utilizes. Normally through the course of utilizing the API they will be the codes that it will return for specific scenarios. Each API method is capable of returning most of these HTTP Codes.</p>
                </div>
                <table class="table table-bordered ">
